name: Mesmerize
description:
what is it about her gaze
that you find so hypnotic?

is it that she seems to peer
straight into your soul
so that your secret fantasies 
are laid bare before her eyes?

there is no part of you
that you can hide for her
she sees all 
and judges nothing

she knows what is 
behind your veil
yet remains hidden
behind hers 

the eternal mystery
